keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
map d removeTab
map u restoreTab
unmap <c-y>
unmap <c-e>
unmap <a-f>
map a-f LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewForegroundTab
map { scrollPageUp
map } scrollPageDown

map w scrollUp
map s scrollDown
map a scrollLeft
map d scrollRight
map A goBack
map D goForward
map W previousTab
map S nextTab
map <c-d> scrollPageDown
map <c-u> scrollPageUp

map m toggleMuteTab
